<% content_for :title do %>
  <title>We've released a new level of Mouse Trapped!</title>
<% end %>

<% content_for :content do %>
  <p>There's a new level of Mouse Trapped online and ready to play. Be one of the first to have a go and perhaps tell us what you think.</p>

  <p><a href="<%= Figaro.env.server_domain %>play?lvl=<%= @level_code.code %>"><button>Play the Level Now</button></a></p>

  <p>Alternatively, use the following level code on the main menu by clicking "resume", or during the game by pressing the Q key.</p>

  <table>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: right; font-weight: bold;">Level Code:</td>
      <td style="text-align: left;"><%= @level_code.code %></td>
    </tr>
  </table>
<% end %>
